        <Parent_String>polyisoprene [300014397], elastomer by composition or origin [300166932], elastomer [300014379], organic material [300011792], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
